ity, $Y$. Our findings\nsuggest that the latter approximation is valid only in cases where the system\nunder study is close to equilibrium, and hence should be used with caution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Dec 2016 20:14:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Jan 2017 18:18:26 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 15 Mar 2017 01:06:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-16"}
