nt today can be hindered due to\nmetal accretion. Peculiar enrichment patterns such as those predicted to arise\nfrom pair-instability supernovae could help in disentangling natal and accreted\nmetal content of stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Dec 2016 21:00:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 May 2017 14:33:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-28"}
